HEADWORD: Stoneweed
<hw>Stone"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genus <gen>Lithospermum</gen>, herbs having a
fruit composed of four stony nutlets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

